Flatbush Ave., east side, north from Overbaugh Place. At the right, is seen the cemetery of the Flatlands Dutch Reformed Church.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(2)

1922.

(3)
The same, showing tomb stones of Van Antie Wickof, wife of Van
Steven Schenck, and Van Steven Schenck.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
